# Unionfind

[![Docs.rs](https://img.shields.io/badge/docs.rs-unionfind-66c2a5?style=for-the-badge&labelColor=555555&logoColor=white&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,)](https://docs.rs/unionfind)
[![Crates.io](https://img.shields.io/crates/v/unionfind?logo=rust&style=for-the-badge)](https://crates.io/crates/unionfind)
